WEBVTT

00:00.174 --> 00:05.122
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:06.094 --> 00:08.802
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.934 --> 00:13.942
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.966 --> 00:18.722
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.758 --> 00:22.786
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.790 --> 00:27.734
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.758 --> 00:31.030
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:31.054 --> 00:34.518
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.542 --> 00:39.790
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.790 --> 00:41.408
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.408 --> 00:44.886
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.910 --> 00:48.182
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.206 --> 00:53.878
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.902 --> 00:55.246
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.246 --> 00:58.582
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.606 --> 01:01.954
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:02.062 --> 01:07.259
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.259 --> 01:08.942
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.942 --> 01:12.342
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.366 --> 01:15.766
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.790 --> 01:21.366
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.390 --> 01:24.802
♪ I love you ♪

01:27.080 --> 01:27.870
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.870 --> 01:30.754
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 6=

01:30.754 --> 01:35.286
(Just the two of us visit the exhibit
on Valentine's Day.)

01:39.890 --> 01:43.310
I sang several songs
when live streaming.

01:54.450 --> 01:56.730
I brought you guys a lot of snacks.

01:56.730 --> 01:59.789
Look, you must be tired
after live-streaming, right?

02:02.409 --> 02:03.750
So many, see?

02:05.569 --> 02:09.949
Pork jerky, dried mango, and chips.

02:13.129 --> 02:17.470
Isn't there anything else
you want to tell us?

02:22.689 --> 02:26.330
Stop staring at me.
Just recording a song for business.

02:26.330 --> 02:27.810
That's it.

02:27.810 --> 02:31.509
That's it?
My idol came to our live room.

02:33.090 --> 02:35.030
Maybe...

02:38.370 --> 02:41.689
He wanted to talk to me
about the song we recorded today.

02:41.689 --> 02:44.109
And his phone died,
so he couldn't say it.

02:45.490 --> 02:47.189
That must be the case.

02:49.090 --> 02:51.474
Well, I'm going back to school. Bye.

02:52.050 --> 02:53.629
I'll send you.

02:54.409 --> 02:56.370
I haven't finished asking
and you're already leaving.

02:56.370 --> 02:58.090
What? Bye. Bye. Bye.

02:58.090 --> 02:58.650
You...

02:58.650 --> 02:59.729
Bye. Bye. Bye.

02:59.729 --> 03:00.370
Helmet.

03:00.370 --> 03:02.990
Avoiding. She's definitely avoiding it.

03:10.289 --> 03:11.729
While you were singing,

03:11.729 --> 03:13.210
I checked up on Qiang Qingci.

03:13.210 --> 03:15.909
No skeletons in the closet.
He's a nice person.

03:16.810 --> 03:19.090
He's always been a good person.

03:19.090 --> 03:21.530
Otherwise, he couldn't have been popular
for so many years.

03:21.530 --> 03:23.729
It doesn't matter to me how he is.

03:23.729 --> 03:26.258
I'm just worried about you
since you made new friends.

03:26.849 --> 03:28.389
Now I'm reassured.

03:29.569 --> 03:30.930
Let's go.

03:41.490 --> 03:43.189
(Have you arrived at the dorm?)

03:46.609 --> 03:47.870
Just sent.

03:49.922 --> 03:51.129
(Perfect Voice_Qiang Qingci)

03:51.129 --> 03:53.770
(On the way walking
a girl back to her school, )

03:53.770 --> 03:55.050
(I saw this.)

03:55.050 --> 03:58.174
(It reminded me of the song
I kept listening to)

03:58.174 --> 04:00.330
(for a campus movie)

04:00.330 --> 04:01.669
(I worked on.)

04:02.238 --> 04:04.490
♪ Through the mountains and waters,
frost fell on the windows ♪

04:04.490 --> 04:08.090
♪ Slowly, with longing and disquiet ♪

04:08.090 --> 04:15.330
♪ Figures on the path pair up at dusk ♪

04:15.330 --> 04:17.909
♪ Tenderness overflows ♪

04:18.849 --> 04:22.090
The photo is from our school,
and the lyrics mention "Shengshengman."

04:22.090 --> 04:25.309
If you say he's not into you,
I honestly won't buy it.

04:26.210 --> 04:29.130
This is his alma mater.
Posting a photo is normal.

04:29.130 --> 04:31.809
And there are many songs
with "Shengshengman" in the lyrics.

04:31.809 --> 04:33.809
You don't believe me.
I'll find one for you.

04:33.809 --> 04:35.289
Fine. I believe you, all right?

04:35.289 --> 04:37.890
He has no interest in you indeed.

04:37.890 --> 04:40.770
Taking a 20-ish stop bus ride back
is just out of politeness.

04:40.770 --> 04:42.690
Posting on Weibo is for the alma mater.

04:42.690 --> 04:44.590
The lyrics fitting is just.

04:45.409 --> 04:48.049
A coincidence. A pure coincidence.

04:48.049 --> 04:52.094
That's my alma mater.
I took a rare photo when I went back.

04:52.094 --> 04:53.909
Why are you all interpreting so much?

04:54.489 --> 04:56.409
Alma mater. Alma mater.

04:56.409 --> 04:58.738
Trying to silence us?

04:59.294 --> 05:01.150
Then...

05:02.849 --> 05:05.409
Sour soup with pig's trotters
for tonight's supper.

05:05.409 --> 05:07.429
Having another meal.

05:12.650 --> 05:15.858
(Did he do it on purpose
or inadvertently?)

05:16.450 --> 05:20.229
(If this goes on,
everyone will misunderstand.)

05:35.770 --> 05:37.309
Smells really good.

05:44.130 --> 05:47.150
I don't know whether I might
venture to ask you a question.

05:48.210 --> 05:51.749
No, if it's a personal question.

05:52.489 --> 05:55.109
But I just want to ask
this personal question today.

05:56.809 --> 05:58.194
You're serious, huh?

05:58.729 --> 06:00.169
What?

06:00.169 --> 06:01.749
You know what I mean.

06:02.609 --> 06:05.490
You know the answer. Then why ask?

06:06.090 --> 06:07.590
I know the answer?

06:16.894 --> 06:18.749
Good. I will take a photo.

06:27.890 --> 06:29.390
He made it.

06:34.489 --> 06:36.450
Are you happy meeting Shengshengman?

06:36.450 --> 06:37.989
Are you eating or not?

06:40.090 --> 06:42.890
You can chat but don't always gossip.

06:42.890 --> 06:45.970
Fine. No kidding.
Answer me a serious question.

06:45.970 --> 06:48.510
When will you meet next time?

06:49.289 --> 06:51.450
We probably won't meet again.

06:51.450 --> 06:52.830
Impossible.

06:53.570 --> 06:55.109
The song is done.

06:57.169 --> 06:58.729
This is just the beginning.

06:58.729 --> 07:00.530
We still have cooperation
with Perfect Voice.

07:00.530 --> 07:04.190
You might meet again soon.

07:20.010 --> 07:23.830
There's only one piece left.
Who will eat it?

07:26.530 --> 07:30.330
Let me check. You've had four pieces.

07:30.330 --> 07:32.609
Juemei ate four pieces.

07:32.609 --> 07:33.729
Both of us had three pieces.

07:33.729 --> 07:36.789
Enough. Stop talking. You eat it.

07:37.330 --> 07:39.150
That would be so impolite.

07:43.690 --> 07:46.429
Look? Didn't I tell you to stop talking?
Now there's none left.

07:48.330 --> 07:51.450
Rarely found a chance
to ask Qiang Qingci to cook.

07:51.450 --> 07:54.738
You were even being polite.
Fake courtesy.

07:55.489 --> 07:58.090
We finally had the goods on Mr. Qiang.

07:58.090 --> 07:59.530
We should blackmail him for a big meal.

07:59.530 --> 08:01.249
We were dismissed

08:01.249 --> 08:02.929
by this trotter soup. It's a big loss.

08:02.929 --> 08:05.270
It's good enough
to have something to eat.

08:06.049 --> 08:08.849
Zhou Zheng, when did he meet Sheng?

08:08.849 --> 08:10.349
Haven't heard you mention it.

08:10.890 --> 08:12.049
I don't know either.

08:12.049 --> 08:13.169
Don't you two live together?

08:13.169 --> 08:13.809
Indeed.

08:13.809 --> 08:15.210
He hasn't told me even though we do.

08:15.210 --> 08:17.169
Didn't you know to observe a bit?

08:17.169 --> 08:19.282
What a waste.
Living together for nothing.

08:19.929 --> 08:21.070
Enough.

08:23.290 --> 08:24.690
Work after your meal.

08:24.690 --> 08:25.810
I haven't eaten enough yet.

08:25.810 --> 08:26.930
Stop nonsense.

08:27.570 --> 08:28.529
Is there any more?

08:28.529 --> 08:29.609
No more.

08:29.609 --> 08:31.550
Finish the soup.

08:32.290 --> 08:35.570
(Wangjia Supermarket)

08:37.769 --> 08:39.009
Seeing a doctor is hard.

08:39.009 --> 08:40.249
Welcome.

08:40.249 --> 08:42.249
I've been queuing till now
and haven't had lunch.

08:42.249 --> 08:45.249
I'm so hungry. My head is spinning.
This bread is not bad.

08:45.249 --> 08:45.930
Pretty good.

08:45.930 --> 08:47.330
Which doctor's appointment did you make?

08:47.330 --> 08:48.849
Mo Qingcheng.

08:48.849 --> 08:51.529
Mo Qingcheng?
The doctor seems too young.

08:51.529 --> 08:53.330
Why don't you
make an appointment with a specialist?

08:53.330 --> 08:55.170
Although he's young,

08:55.170 --> 08:57.330
many people recommended him to me.

08:57.330 --> 09:00.090
I saw him today and it was really good.
Good medical skills.

09:00.090 --> 09:00.369
Really?

09:00.369 --> 09:02.354
His attitude is good. Very attentive.

09:03.070 --> 09:03.450
Twelve.

09:03.450 --> 09:04.410
Let me pay.

09:04.410 --> 09:05.869
I'll pay.

09:07.729 --> 09:08.769
See you next time.

09:08.769 --> 09:11.310
Let's dig in. I'm so dizzy from hunger.

09:15.490 --> 09:17.746
(Wangjia Supermarket)

09:21.690 --> 09:25.050
Young boss. You look so happy.
Did you win a lottery?

09:25.050 --> 09:28.930
No. I just heard them saying
which doctor is good.

09:28.930 --> 09:30.649
The shop is right opposite the hospital.

09:30.649 --> 09:33.109
Aren't you fed up
listening to it every day?

09:34.050 --> 09:39.090
Listen, the most frequent visitors
to our shop are doctors,

09:39.090 --> 09:40.810
patients and their families.

09:40.810 --> 09:43.210
The words we often heard are

09:43.210 --> 09:45.889
the long waiting list of beds,

09:45.889 --> 09:47.649
the doctors' gossip,

09:47.649 --> 09:49.889
and something about
the specialist outpatient clinic.

09:49.889 --> 09:51.609
And such, anyway.

09:51.609 --> 09:54.649
By the way, are you leaving
when your cousin comes later?

09:54.649 --> 09:57.070
Yes. I bought a movie ticket, at 7 PM.

09:59.090 --> 10:00.210
Who are you with?

10:01.129 --> 10:03.269
Me alone. A single ticket.

10:03.810 --> 10:06.729
Alone? Let me know next time
and I'll go with you.

10:06.729 --> 10:08.310
Okay. I'll call you next time.

10:11.210 --> 10:13.129
Let me answer a WeChat message.

10:13.129 --> 10:15.050
Okay. Since there's no consumer,
you can go ahead.

10:15.050 --> 10:16.274
Thank you.

10:25.009 --> 10:28.330
Listen, our idol has been
really high-profile lately.

10:28.330 --> 10:30.369
He released a song directly.
You know what the point is?

10:30.369 --> 10:33.889
The point is he's included
Shengshengman in his lyrics.

10:33.889 --> 10:36.790
How far have those two developed?

10:37.489 --> 10:40.369
But, you know,
he's been so popular these past years.

10:40.369 --> 10:44.109
Him being high-profile for once
might mean he's found true love.

10:48.450 --> 10:50.330
I just love whatever relates to him.

10:50.330 --> 10:52.450
As long as he likes her and he's happy,

10:52.450 --> 10:54.970
I'm all for it. Listen, as long as

10:54.970 --> 10:57.670
he doesn't get dumped tomorrow
after being together today.

11:03.529 --> 11:05.509
(Doomed.)

11:08.489 --> 11:09.889
(He can't speak.)

11:09.889 --> 11:13.190
(Yiru will definitely recognize
his voice as Qiang Qingci.)

11:15.249 --> 11:17.389
Hello.

11:19.690 --> 11:22.349
Welcome.

11:26.290 --> 11:27.749
What can I help you with?

11:28.810 --> 11:30.029
I know!

11:32.810 --> 11:34.670
I know what he's going to buy.

11:35.970 --> 11:36.989
Over there.

11:43.649 --> 11:44.970
A regular customer?

11:44.970 --> 11:47.430
Right. A regular customer
who comes every day.

11:49.690 --> 11:51.229
Send your WeChat messages.

11:55.450 --> 11:58.349
She's your fan. She would recognize
your voice as you speak.

12:04.849 --> 12:07.090
Take whatever you like.

12:07.090 --> 12:10.009
Tell you what. Shengshengman
just has too few fans.

12:10.009 --> 12:12.649
She's even been mocked
for clinging to a big shot.

12:12.649 --> 12:14.690
I was so angry back then.

12:14.690 --> 12:16.290
She's a composer
who works behind the scenes.

12:16.290 --> 12:18.930
How about going out?

12:18.930 --> 12:20.869
I'll bring it to the front for you.

12:26.170 --> 12:28.769
Anyway, I like whomever my idol likes.

12:28.769 --> 12:30.470
I support him unconditionally.

12:45.970 --> 12:47.769
Your fan seems to
have some misunderstandings.

12:47.769 --> 12:49.830
I didn't tell her I am Shengshengman.

12:50.889 --> 12:51.849
I know.

12:51.849 --> 12:53.090
She's a huge fan of yours.

12:53.090 --> 12:54.690
She has listened to all your shows.

12:54.690 --> 12:56.249
And she's especially nice.

12:56.249 --> 12:58.690
So, when I come to
the supermarket again in the future,

12:58.690 --> 13:00.389
I can't say half a word.

13:02.410 --> 13:04.609
If you don't want to be exposed,

13:04.609 --> 13:07.210
and have your fans
come to the hospital to spectate,

13:07.210 --> 13:09.149
I suggest you remain silent.

13:10.769 --> 13:12.930
Alright. Silence is golden.

13:12.930 --> 13:15.090
But it's not like
she's going to be here all the time.

13:15.090 --> 13:17.009
My dad, my mom, and my cousin

13:17.009 --> 13:18.889
will take turns staying here.

13:18.889 --> 13:20.950
It's fine when the others are here.

13:25.450 --> 13:28.529
Do you want anything else
besides drinks?

13:28.529 --> 13:31.989
Boxed meals.
Your boxed meals are very good.

13:32.489 --> 13:35.070
They are handmade by my mom.
Not wholesaled.

13:35.070 --> 13:37.050
Definitely genuine.

13:37.050 --> 13:39.849
Really? Auntie's craftsmanship
is truly impressive.

13:39.849 --> 13:41.729
Wait here. I'll go get it.

13:41.729 --> 13:42.950
My treat.

13:51.769 --> 13:53.690
I come here often.

13:53.690 --> 13:55.369
You can't treat me every day.

13:55.369 --> 13:59.989
You treated me to bamboo shoot soup.
Now I should reciprocate.

14:01.129 --> 14:01.930
Thank you.

14:01.930 --> 14:03.190
Then let me get it.

14:03.902 --> 14:06.386
(Business Hours)

14:09.849 --> 14:11.430
Boxed meal.

14:23.729 --> 14:25.869
Excuse me, please make way. Thank you.

14:37.050 --> 14:39.710
Get a bag for these, and this.

14:40.889 --> 14:42.849
But you have to
keep track of these things.

14:42.849 --> 14:44.529
Otherwise, your mom will ask.

14:44.529 --> 14:46.790
Just record them.
You can say I ate them all.

14:49.410 --> 14:52.029
Got it. Indeed, he's pretty handsome.

14:53.050 --> 14:55.249
Whether he is handsome or not
has nothing to do with me.

14:55.249 --> 14:58.290
Yet you feed him with your own goods.

14:58.290 --> 14:59.849
He treated me to a meal last time.

14:59.849 --> 15:02.070
This is me reciprocating. Bye.

15:04.330 --> 15:07.509
Reciprocating? What was she taking?

15:13.649 --> 15:15.910
Cousin! You're here.

15:17.529 --> 15:19.762
What do you need that bag for, Sheng?

15:20.369 --> 15:21.389
Snacks.

15:25.210 --> 15:26.450
Cousin, is your moped dead?

15:26.450 --> 15:27.609
Let me go get you a power strip.

15:27.609 --> 15:29.410
No, thanks. I charged it yesterday.

15:29.410 --> 15:30.570
A charge lasts over 100 kilometers.

15:30.570 --> 15:31.649
It can still go a long way.

15:31.649 --> 15:32.810
Okay, then I'm leaving.

15:32.810 --> 15:33.889
Wait a moment.

15:33.889 --> 15:36.882
Isn't that the doctor
you were into last time?

15:37.529 --> 15:40.690
I was not into anyone. I think he's nice
as he protected his colleagues.

15:40.690 --> 15:42.210
And I wanted to give him a discount.

15:42.210 --> 15:43.889
Then the physiognomy...

15:43.889 --> 15:45.529
What physiognomy? You can go.

15:45.529 --> 15:46.889
I'll go now. Bye-bye.

15:46.889 --> 15:47.649
Be careful.

15:47.649 --> 15:49.070
Bye-bye.

15:51.529 --> 15:52.710
Dong Yiru.

16:07.649 --> 16:08.670
Come here.

16:13.450 --> 16:16.690
I saw you defending your colleague
at the hospital entrance last time.

16:16.690 --> 16:18.970
I joked about it with my cousin.

16:18.970 --> 16:21.202
He was talking nonsense.
Just ignore him.

16:22.249 --> 16:24.670
You saw it?

16:26.649 --> 16:29.970
Yes. That was my fifth cousin.

16:29.970 --> 16:32.769
Fifth cousin? You have a lot of cousins?

16:32.769 --> 16:35.310
Yes, five of them. He's the youngest.

16:38.450 --> 16:41.249
This is the boxed meal.
And a lot of snacks.

16:41.249 --> 16:42.489
They are all delicious. Try some.

16:42.489 --> 16:43.869
That's a lot.

16:45.210 --> 16:46.450
Thank you.

16:52.129 --> 16:54.269
It's time for you
to go back to the hospital.

16:54.930 --> 16:57.746
I still have some time. What about you?

16:58.410 --> 17:01.509
I don't have classes this week.
I'm helping out in the store.

17:03.289 --> 17:05.989
So, you are available now?

17:07.198 --> 17:08.306
Yes.

17:08.890 --> 17:10.509
Let me treat you to coffee.

17:12.970 --> 17:14.269
Bubble tea is also fine.

17:17.009 --> 17:18.670
Bubble tea.

17:19.850 --> 17:21.769
I see there's a bubble tea shop ahead.

17:21.769 --> 17:23.029
Let's go for it.

17:26.970 --> 17:28.178
Let's go.

17:36.706 --> 17:38.569
(Wangjia Supermarket)

17:38.569 --> 17:40.210
Your cousin's boyfriend-to-be.

17:40.210 --> 17:41.269
Him?

17:42.610 --> 17:46.610
How handsome. You don't approve of him?

17:46.610 --> 17:48.210
It's not that.

17:48.210 --> 17:50.630
I'm just curious how they met.

17:51.329 --> 17:52.809
Simply by shopping, right?

17:52.809 --> 17:54.729
Buy a drink today,
and a boxed meal tomorrow.

17:54.729 --> 17:56.549
It led to familiarity, didn't it?

17:57.970 --> 18:00.170
How come no one is familiar with me?

18:00.170 --> 18:02.970
I'm not bad-looking, either.

18:02.970 --> 18:05.110
Why not reflect on yourself?

18:17.009 --> 18:19.610
We eat at night...

18:19.610 --> 18:20.489
Dr. Mo.

18:20.489 --> 18:22.049
Dr. Mo.

18:22.049 --> 18:22.890
Working the night shift?

18:22.890 --> 18:23.910
Yes.

18:25.089 --> 18:26.110
See you.

18:26.970 --> 18:27.729
Let's go.

18:27.729 --> 18:29.049
Hurry up. Look.

18:29.049 --> 18:30.162
Do you see it?

18:32.569 --> 18:34.229
I'm also working the night shift.

18:35.370 --> 18:38.130
It's really tough.
There are doctors in my family, too.

18:38.130 --> 18:39.729
Both my grandparents are doctors.

18:39.729 --> 18:42.950
Sometimes they're not even around
for New Year's Eve dinner.

18:44.970 --> 18:46.430
Will you be here tonight?

18:47.890 --> 18:51.269
Yes. What?

18:53.289 --> 18:57.509
Just asking. Maybe I'll bump into you
if I come over tonight.

18:58.489 --> 18:59.989
I see.

19:01.130 --> 19:02.589
That should be possible.

19:04.410 --> 19:05.589
Well, I have to go.

19:06.610 --> 19:07.289
Bye-bye.

19:07.289 --> 19:08.402
Bye-bye.

19:15.458 --> 19:17.330
(Please cross at the zebra crossing)

19:30.970 --> 19:33.850
What are you looking at?
Why aren't you going home?

19:33.850 --> 19:35.610
I'm staying to work the night shift.

19:35.610 --> 19:38.410
Why? Aren't you going to the movie?

19:38.410 --> 19:40.630
No. It's too crowded.
I don't want to watch.

19:41.690 --> 19:43.269
Don't watch it as it's crowded?

19:44.289 --> 19:45.789
It smells so good.

19:48.249 --> 19:49.670
No one's here.

19:59.394 --> 20:02.354
(Wangjia Supermarket)

20:08.049 --> 20:08.650
He's coming.

20:08.650 --> 20:09.089
Who's coming?

20:09.089 --> 20:10.190
Look.

20:10.890 --> 20:12.630
Is he coming to our store?

20:17.529 --> 20:18.870
He entered.

20:23.769 --> 20:26.509
Hello, welcome. May I help you?

20:27.569 --> 20:29.910
I know! I know what you want.

20:31.650 --> 20:33.789
I know. You don't need to talk.

20:35.210 --> 20:38.269
So strict. She doesn't
even allow him to talk to girls.

20:43.850 --> 20:46.130
Work. What are you doing here?

20:46.130 --> 20:47.910
Go to work. What are you doing?

20:53.529 --> 20:55.069
Grab a bag.

21:05.009 --> 21:06.309
Just take a quick look.

21:12.569 --> 21:14.729
54.5 and a 15-yuan boxed meal.

21:14.729 --> 21:17.470
Total is 69.5.
How would you like to pay?

21:18.769 --> 21:20.018
Okay.

21:21.930 --> 21:23.430
Please wait for a while.

21:28.009 --> 21:30.589
Here's your receipt. Thank you.

21:46.170 --> 21:50.690
Why isn't this guy talking today?
What does that mean?

21:50.690 --> 21:53.870
Stop looking. Go to work.

21:54.370 --> 21:55.710
Stop looking.

22:09.210 --> 22:12.670
(Moqingcheng)
(No time for chit chat. Talk later.)

22:46.970 --> 22:48.229
Peanut.

22:49.249 --> 22:50.710
I

22:52.529 --> 22:54.910
like someone's voice.

22:55.610 --> 23:00.910
But now, I kind of feel...

23:03.130 --> 23:05.069
It seems he feels
something for me as well.

23:07.729 --> 23:11.710
Am I overthinking?

23:15.850 --> 23:18.470
If I've overthought,
it would be awkward, wouldn't it?

23:22.009 --> 23:24.190
It would be awkward if I've overthought.

23:26.729 --> 23:29.430
Forget it. You wouldn't understand it.

23:34.370 --> 23:36.870
It is so late. You want me
to get scolded with you.

23:40.210 --> 23:44.018
I can't keep on eating
if I can't fall asleep this late.

23:44.690 --> 23:46.190
What should I do?

23:49.210 --> 23:50.789
What about having some fruit?

23:52.249 --> 23:53.394
Go.

24:03.729 --> 24:05.509
Shengshengman.

24:08.089 --> 24:09.370
No shouting my nickname in public.

24:09.370 --> 24:10.850
Treat me to a meal.

24:10.850 --> 24:12.210
Again?

24:12.210 --> 24:13.729
Your school has been completely exposed.

24:13.729 --> 24:15.329
What if everyone organizes

24:15.329 --> 24:16.970
an event to find Shengshengman?

24:16.970 --> 24:18.670
You'll have to buy my silence.

24:19.729 --> 24:22.950
Valentine's Day is coming, Sheng.

24:24.089 --> 24:26.489
Yeah, Valentine's Day
is around the corner.

24:26.489 --> 24:30.850
Okay. We can consider it
as a Valentine's gift for the fans.

24:30.850 --> 24:32.930
Right. Valentine's Day is coming soon.

24:32.930 --> 24:36.269
How about "Return With You"?

24:37.009 --> 24:38.870
Are you thinking of Qiang Qingci?

24:40.170 --> 24:41.269
No.

24:42.809 --> 24:43.910
I'll take a call.

24:52.569 --> 24:53.589
(Hi.)

24:56.089 --> 24:58.430
(I want to ask about that song.)

25:06.930 --> 25:08.210
Let's go.

25:08.210 --> 25:09.298
Let's go.

25:13.249 --> 25:14.809
Dr. Mo, you just finished checking?

25:14.809 --> 25:18.170
Yes. Bed number three and bed number ten
can be discharged tomorrow.

25:18.170 --> 25:19.809
Great. Their family members
ask me every day.

25:19.809 --> 25:21.130
I'll go my rounds this morning. See you.

25:21.130 --> 25:22.258
Okay.

25:23.130 --> 25:24.249
Excuse me, I want that fish.

25:24.249 --> 25:25.330
Okay.

25:28.970 --> 25:30.089
Thank you.

25:30.089 --> 25:31.090
Okay.

25:31.610 --> 25:33.009
Sheng, let's sit over there.

25:33.009 --> 25:33.210
Okay.

25:33.210 --> 25:34.390
I'll get a drink.

25:40.170 --> 25:41.809
Mr. Mo, I'm going to the ward.

25:41.809 --> 25:42.898
There you go.

25:44.489 --> 25:45.618
(Hi.)

25:52.329 --> 25:55.229
There's a games carnival.
Do you want to go?

26:15.049 --> 26:18.890
I have always wanted to see it.

26:18.890 --> 26:20.670
I have never been there.

26:21.210 --> 26:24.749
But, aren't you very busy?

26:28.650 --> 26:30.630
I'm not busy that day.

26:41.569 --> 26:43.029
Did the tutor need you?

26:44.569 --> 26:45.630
No.

26:57.489 --> 26:58.610
Okay.

27:02.410 --> 27:05.390
Alright. I will pick you up on Sunday.

27:09.569 --> 27:10.809
(Okay.)

27:10.809 --> 27:14.309
Sunday.

27:19.426 --> 27:21.010
(14th. Sunday. Valentine's Day)

27:21.289 --> 27:24.950
(Sunday. February 14th.
Valentine's Day.)

27:43.930 --> 27:46.470
What's wrong? Is everything okay?

27:47.970 --> 27:49.229
Nothing.

28:08.170 --> 28:09.710
Is the rice so delicious?

28:10.970 --> 28:12.670
Eat your vegetables, Sheng.

28:31.529 --> 28:33.950
I'm exhausted and you can still laugh.

28:36.650 --> 28:39.049
It's not your first day knowing
that we're busy in Cardiothoracic.

28:39.049 --> 28:41.850
Have you scheduled the weekend?

28:41.850 --> 28:43.249
Off.

28:43.249 --> 28:44.450
Just in time for Valentine's Day.

28:44.450 --> 28:47.130
I planned to have a meal
with other department's singles.

28:47.130 --> 28:49.710
After all, it's a festival. Come along.

28:50.329 --> 28:52.829
I will pass. I have plans that day.

28:56.249 --> 28:58.670
Valentine's Day. Something happened?

29:01.489 --> 29:02.610
Mr. Zhou.

29:02.610 --> 29:02.850
Hello.

29:02.850 --> 29:04.049
Looking sharp today.

29:04.049 --> 29:05.910
When do I not look smart?

29:08.529 --> 29:11.289
Zhou Zheng, perfect timing.

29:11.289 --> 29:13.450
Here is the collaboration agreement
with that app.

29:13.450 --> 29:14.890
Could you deliver it when you have time?

29:14.890 --> 29:16.930
I've already signed and sealed it.

29:16.930 --> 29:17.970
Just find a deliveryman.

29:17.970 --> 29:19.049
Why me?

29:19.049 --> 29:22.229
No. You must drive it there.
It's not far anyway.

29:25.089 --> 29:27.509
Fine. I'll let her know.

29:37.650 --> 29:40.229
(Xingfu, are you free to meet?)

29:41.210 --> 29:42.749
(What do you want to meet for?)

29:44.249 --> 29:47.350
(Of course, to discuss the contract.)

29:52.210 --> 29:55.630
So, it's about the contract.
Just send it by courier.

29:57.569 --> 30:01.029
That's what I said, silly Doudou.

30:04.850 --> 30:09.289
Or how about Sunday?
I just happen to be going downtown then.

30:09.289 --> 30:11.150
Let's get in touch then.

30:15.210 --> 30:16.749
Sunday?

30:19.850 --> 30:21.106
(Okay.)

30:25.970 --> 30:28.430
Which day of the week is Sunday?
What date is it?

30:35.618 --> 30:36.850
(14th. Valentine's Day)

30:40.009 --> 30:42.029
No way.

30:43.809 --> 30:45.930
It can't be.

30:45.930 --> 30:47.069
What's up?

30:49.610 --> 30:55.489
Doudou, would you meet alone
with a regular friend

30:55.489 --> 30:57.749
on Valentine's Day?

30:59.009 --> 31:00.749
I'm not interested in you.

31:01.249 --> 31:03.509
What do you mean?
I'm not interested in you either.

31:10.370 --> 31:11.230
We're back.

31:11.230 --> 31:14.390
Zhou Zheng, is there any coffee left?

31:15.809 --> 31:18.670
Dressed so smartly?
Not a single cup left.

31:22.650 --> 31:25.850
What about the milk?
Why is there no milk?

31:25.850 --> 31:27.729
I used it for coffee this morning.

31:27.729 --> 31:28.850
So how do I make my coffee?

31:28.850 --> 31:31.390
Just make do with the instant stuff.

31:42.370 --> 31:43.742
What's going on here?

31:43.742 --> 31:45.302
Missing a girl?

31:47.529 --> 31:49.190
It's not that simple.

31:50.009 --> 31:50.769
How so?

31:50.769 --> 31:52.809
No? Tell us in detail.

31:52.809 --> 31:53.729
I'm all ears.

31:53.729 --> 31:54.410
Feel free to speak.

31:54.410 --> 31:55.170
An attentive listener.

31:55.170 --> 31:57.074
Listener. Listeners get their share.

31:57.729 --> 31:59.170
Strive for improvement.

31:59.170 --> 32:01.410
Improvement... You got me.

32:01.410 --> 32:03.650
Off you go. You two can leave.

32:03.650 --> 32:04.789
Don't bother me.

32:05.450 --> 32:06.829
Come on. Tell us.

32:07.650 --> 32:09.009
Fine. There's a secret now.

32:09.009 --> 32:10.410
How hypocritical.

32:10.410 --> 32:12.229
Imposing on someone.

32:14.569 --> 32:16.970
Someone makes it harder for someone.

32:16.970 --> 32:19.549
Isn't that a detour then? Again.

32:22.890 --> 32:24.150
It's sent out.

32:25.329 --> 32:28.009
Sorry. Wang Ke played with my phone

32:28.009 --> 32:29.910
and sent a blank message.

32:30.769 --> 32:33.710
Who played with your phone?
You deceived.

32:36.009 --> 32:39.509
Never mind. I am free only that day.
Are you okay with it?

32:43.370 --> 32:46.526
Yes. See you then.

32:46.526 --> 32:47.089
Then I...

32:47.089 --> 32:48.989
Geng Xiaoxing.

32:50.729 --> 32:54.170
I want to share a juicy gossip with you.

32:54.170 --> 32:56.329
Go ahead. What's the gossip?

32:56.329 --> 33:00.650
This Sunday, that man
is planning to meet with Sheng.

33:00.650 --> 33:03.430
They seem to be making great progress.
Going on a date again.

33:04.529 --> 33:06.370
Is that all you have to say?

33:06.370 --> 33:08.089
Well, what else should I react with?

33:08.089 --> 33:12.150
It's Valentine's Day this Sunday.

33:16.170 --> 33:17.690
They are indeed going out for a date.

33:17.690 --> 33:21.289
Yes. I'm so excited.

33:21.289 --> 33:23.489
They are dating on Valentine's Day.

33:23.489 --> 33:25.769
Could it be that Qiang
is going to confess his love?

33:25.769 --> 33:27.890
Or is it Sheng who's going to confess?

33:27.890 --> 33:29.970
Regardless of who confesses,
it's bound to be successful.

33:29.970 --> 33:33.269
Oh, no. There's a big misunderstanding.

33:36.866 --> 33:38.610
(14th. Valentine's Day)

33:38.610 --> 33:41.069
Finally, Valentine's Day is here.

33:42.089 --> 33:44.809
You even mark it.
Do you also have a date?

33:44.809 --> 33:45.910
No, I don't.

33:46.410 --> 33:48.950
What's up? You do?

33:49.890 --> 33:50.994
I don't.

33:52.410 --> 33:53.970
Yet, you're grinning.

33:53.970 --> 33:57.250
You are already a well-known singer
with two million fans.

33:57.250 --> 33:59.529
Can't you sort out
your personal problems?

33:59.529 --> 34:01.169
Do you really have the nerve
to say that to me?

34:01.169 --> 34:03.569
Aren't you also famous
in the traditional music circle?

34:03.569 --> 34:06.330
Well-off and even investing, huh?

34:06.330 --> 34:07.250
Aren't you single as well?

34:07.250 --> 34:08.290
I'm happy.

34:08.290 --> 34:09.350
I'm happy too.

34:10.689 --> 34:13.870
♪ If you're happy and you know it,
clap your hands ♪

34:14.410 --> 34:17.290
♪ If you're happy and you know it,
clap your hands ♪

34:17.290 --> 34:19.129
What's making you so cheerful?

34:19.129 --> 34:20.290
It's a festival.

34:20.290 --> 34:21.509
A festival.

34:24.450 --> 34:27.370
Mr. Mo, what shall we cook tonight?

34:27.370 --> 34:29.890
I'm going home tonight
and won't live here.

34:29.890 --> 34:31.390
You're not living here?

34:32.290 --> 34:33.509
Go on being happy.

34:35.089 --> 34:36.169
Goodbye, Doudou.

34:36.169 --> 34:36.689
Bye-bye.

34:36.689 --> 34:37.746
Bye-bye.

34:38.609 --> 34:40.730
His relationship
is developing too rapidly.

34:40.730 --> 34:43.129
I can't keep up with the pace anymore.

34:43.129 --> 34:46.230
Suddenly, being single
doesn't seem so joyful.

34:47.529 --> 34:49.129
But you have to understand.

34:49.129 --> 34:51.026
Mr. Mo is at that age.

34:51.609 --> 34:53.450
The oldest is still lying inside.

34:53.450 --> 34:55.330
And he's also single.

34:55.330 --> 34:56.709
That makes sense.

34:58.410 --> 34:59.529
You're leaving?

34:59.529 --> 35:00.529
I'll go out.

35:00.529 --> 35:01.649
Then, tonight I might...

35:01.649 --> 35:03.470
Not come back as well?

35:04.970 --> 35:07.330
I might return late.

35:07.330 --> 35:09.750
It's the weekend, so I go to meet
a classmate for a meal.

35:12.129 --> 35:13.009
I'm off. Bye-bye.

35:13.009 --> 35:14.470
So annoying.

35:21.890 --> 35:23.750
What happened? Did he drop something?

35:26.209 --> 35:28.069
Delivering a contract by the way.

35:28.810 --> 35:32.649
What? Don't associate
everything with Valentine's Day.

35:32.649 --> 35:33.669
Bye-bye.

35:35.810 --> 35:38.230
One, two, three. Three, two, one.

35:38.850 --> 35:40.330
I'm not happy either.

35:40.330 --> 35:44.009
Wanting to be happy is simple. Wait.

35:44.009 --> 35:47.850
Mao, here comes a job.

35:47.850 --> 35:50.002
(Girl's Dorm No. 3)

35:58.930 --> 36:02.089
(What if he didn't know
today is Valentine's Day)

36:02.089 --> 36:05.109
(and happened to choose this day? )

36:08.450 --> 36:13.266
(Girl's Dorm)

36:15.426 --> 36:16.606
(Girl's Dorm No. 3)

36:16.606 --> 36:17.209
For you.

36:17.209 --> 36:18.410
Have you been waiting long?

36:18.410 --> 36:19.570
No.

36:22.890 --> 36:23.890
You waited for a while.

36:23.890 --> 36:24.850
What shall we eat tonight?

36:24.850 --> 36:25.810
I just got here. Hot pot.

36:25.810 --> 36:26.209
Hot pot.

36:26.209 --> 36:26.810
Anywhere you like.

36:26.810 --> 36:27.689
No. Let's choose another.

36:27.689 --> 36:29.270
Who are you waiting for?

36:30.810 --> 36:31.830
Gu Sheng.

36:38.330 --> 36:39.910
Gu Sheng.

36:40.850 --> 36:43.350
Mr. Mo. Senior.

36:44.169 --> 36:47.730
Mo Qingcheng, this is
my junior from university.

36:47.730 --> 36:49.970
You're my senior from high school.

36:49.970 --> 36:51.589
You're my junior from university.

36:52.370 --> 36:56.082
So how should you two sort out
your seniority from now on?

36:58.970 --> 37:00.569
It should start from you.

37:00.569 --> 37:03.410
I'll call her sister-in-law.

37:03.410 --> 37:04.830
Is everything ready?

37:07.410 --> 37:08.254
Then we are leaving.

37:08.254 --> 37:09.790
Senior, take care.

37:10.649 --> 37:11.649
Senior, goodbye.

37:11.649 --> 37:12.754
Let's go.

37:15.569 --> 37:17.629
Is your backpack heavy?
Do you need help?

37:18.410 --> 37:19.570
No, thanks.

37:22.770 --> 37:23.830
What's wrong?

37:26.009 --> 37:29.850
When I see you, I remember
that I still owe someone a lot of music.

37:29.850 --> 37:31.289
Thinking about composing.

37:34.410 --> 37:36.410
There must be many people today.

37:36.410 --> 37:39.589
There are many people on weekends,
and today is even Valentine's Day.

37:43.089 --> 37:44.830
So I drove here.

37:46.489 --> 37:47.529
It's crowded everywhere today.

37:47.529 --> 37:50.194
Without a car, it might be
inconvenient to send you home tonight.

37:50.890 --> 37:54.049
No need. There are subway stations
and bus stops near my home.

37:54.049 --> 37:55.569
It's very convenient.

37:55.569 --> 37:58.310
Get in the car first.
Don't worry about going home now.

38:12.810 --> 38:15.850
(I'm so awkward to bring up
Valentine's Day by myself just now.)

38:15.850 --> 38:17.189
Still holding the bag?

38:19.770 --> 38:21.074
Give it to me.

38:23.970 --> 38:27.009
Is there anything fragile or water?

38:27.009 --> 38:28.029
No.

38:33.169 --> 38:34.430
Seat belt.

38:52.770 --> 38:54.890
It will take a long time on the way.

38:54.890 --> 38:56.950
If you're thirsty, there's water here.

39:02.089 --> 39:03.230
Let's hit the road.

39:19.850 --> 39:22.310
Do we all meet there?

39:23.810 --> 39:28.470
I mean, besides you and me,
Doudou and Juemei.

39:29.970 --> 39:31.310
Only you and me.

39:33.089 --> 39:35.029
They are all busy today.

39:39.169 --> 39:40.989
They are so busy at weekends.

39:42.489 --> 39:45.589
Yeah. I don't know what happened today.

39:46.129 --> 39:49.149
I saw no one early in the morning.

39:54.370 --> 39:57.830
Probably they all
went out and celebrated the festival.

40:00.810 --> 40:01.830
It's possible.

40:10.810 --> 40:15.470
(On Valentine's Day, just the two of us
visit the exhibition.)

40:17.930 --> 40:19.089
Dongfeng.

40:19.089 --> 40:20.009
Dongfeng.

40:20.009 --> 40:23.169
- I'll go now. Happy Valentine's Day.
- Have a good festival.

40:23.169 --> 40:25.649
- Bye-bye.
- Happy Valentine's Day.

40:25.649 --> 40:28.810
Why do I spend
every Valentine's Day with you guys?

40:28.810 --> 40:30.529
Any opinions? Keep it.

40:30.529 --> 40:32.850
I promised to go shopping
with my wife today.

40:32.850 --> 40:34.970
Y-You could tell us earlier.

40:34.970 --> 40:36.330
You can go now.

40:36.330 --> 40:37.489
You should have said it earlier.

40:37.489 --> 40:39.910
She's already out for a facial
with her bestie.

40:40.410 --> 40:41.049
Dongfeng.

40:41.049 --> 40:42.569
I had a date but I canceled it.

40:42.569 --> 40:44.330
Isn't it enough
to play mahjong with you?

40:44.330 --> 40:46.089
What date did you have?

40:46.089 --> 40:50.569
The second daughter
of my mom's former bestie. A blind date.

40:50.569 --> 40:52.250
I'm too embarrassed to say it.

40:52.250 --> 40:53.529
Hongzhong.

40:53.529 --> 40:56.970
Every time she broke up,
I was the big brother who consoled her.

40:56.970 --> 40:59.970
It is too intimate,
so it is impossible to date her.

40:59.970 --> 41:03.629
So close. You can introduce me.

41:09.609 --> 41:12.649
What's wrong with me?
I'm single and free of any encumbrances.

41:12.649 --> 41:14.669
I don't mess around.
I have a stable job.

41:15.529 --> 41:17.989
Except for Mao, who isn't like that?

41:20.569 --> 41:23.730
Fine. Let's cheer for our single life
and keep each other company.

41:23.730 --> 41:25.730
When we get old,
we can put out a sign that says

41:25.730 --> 41:27.730
"Tianzi No. 1 Senior Apartment."

41:27.730 --> 41:30.470
Single apartment. Baiban.

41:42.770 --> 41:45.410
Dr. Mo, it's been a long time.
How rare it is for you to drive back.

41:45.410 --> 41:47.049
I have the day off today. Thank you.

41:47.049 --> 41:48.430
Alright. See you.

41:55.970 --> 41:58.850
(Is this where he lives?)

41:58.850 --> 42:00.270
This is where I live.

42:01.250 --> 42:02.310
What's wrong?

42:04.209 --> 42:05.750
You live here?

42:07.370 --> 42:09.669
This is my residential area.
Of course, I live here.

42:11.370 --> 42:14.589
(Aren't we to visit an exhibit?
How did we end up at his place?)

42:23.850 --> 42:25.250
Thank you.

42:25.250 --> 42:26.410
Have you been here?

42:26.850 --> 42:29.089
No, I just think

42:29.089 --> 42:31.890
you wouldn't let anyone know
your residential address easily.

42:31.890 --> 42:34.750
After all, you don't even
post your photos online.

42:35.410 --> 42:37.390
I indeed wouldn't let outsiders know.

42:40.850 --> 42:42.609
The recording studio
is closer to the hospital,

42:42.609 --> 42:43.970
so I often stay there too.

42:43.970 --> 42:46.169
I also rented a place with Juemei.

42:46.169 --> 42:47.850
I stay there on weekends.

42:47.850 --> 42:50.009
This is where my parents live.

42:50.009 --> 42:51.450
Because it's close to
the exhibition hall.

42:51.450 --> 42:52.790
Parking is convenient.

42:55.089 --> 42:59.209
So you've been living here
since you were a kid.

42:59.209 --> 43:00.466
Right.

43:01.970 --> 43:03.350
It's quite quiet.

43:04.089 --> 43:05.890
Do you want to
write down my phone number?

43:05.890 --> 43:09.189
In case we get separated when packed.
It would be easier to find each other.

43:45.282 --> 43:50.750
♪ Turning the years into a drifting boat ♪

43:50.750 --> 43:56.030
♪ Sailing through
the tumult and winding sorrow ♪

43:56.030 --> 43:57.886
♪ I fear that the past ♪

43:57.886 --> 44:01.470
♪ Will be crushed
by the coming cold wind ♪

44:01.470 --> 44:07.730
♪ And stirred into
a piece of tranquil river water ♪

44:09.730 --> 44:15.134
♪ Touching the crack with my fingertips ♪

44:15.134 --> 44:19.806
♪ I dare not look at the haggard faces
and gray hair in the mirror ♪

44:19.806 --> 44:22.494
♪ After many years ♪

44:22.494 --> 44:25.534
♪ The longing remains as sharp ♪

44:25.534 --> 44:30.654
♪ And our shadows are thinner ♪

44:30.654 --> 44:33.950
♪ Grinding the memories into ink ♪

44:33.950 --> 44:37.054
♪ And writing them on the paper ♪

44:37.054 --> 44:39.006
♪ The mirror and the person
are both gone ♪

44:39.006 --> 44:41.726
♪ Where could I ask for the return date ♪

44:41.726 --> 44:44.958
♪ The bronze mirror shatters at farewell ♪

44:44.958 --> 44:47.198
♪ It's hard to convey the lovesickness ♪

44:47.198 --> 44:52.018
♪ Over millions of miles ♪

44:52.670 --> 44:55.870
♪ I laugh at the fame
and wealth of my life ♪

44:55.870 --> 44:58.142
♪ I picture it as a flower in the mirror ♪

44:58.142 --> 45:02.878
♪ It's hard to rival
a cup of tea in your hand ♪

45:02.878 --> 45:04.702
♪ We drink from the same cup ♪

45:04.702 --> 45:06.814
♪ And we share joy and sorrow ♪

45:06.814 --> 45:09.726
♪ We drink down the past memories ♪

45:09.726 --> 45:14.142
♪ Being together from morning till night ♪

45:14.142 --> 45:17.342
♪ Or alone in the corner of the world ♪

45:17.342 --> 45:19.614
♪ Frost whitens the hair
in front of the forehead ♪

45:19.614 --> 45:24.638
♪ Looking at the world,
where is my home ♪

45:24.638 --> 45:27.198
♪ I wish the clear frost
glitter in the moonlight ♪

45:27.198 --> 45:30.878
♪ Reflecting the couple in the mirror ♪

45:30.878 --> 45:36.434
♪ Return with you ♪

45:37.118 --> 45:43.026
♪ After being separated for half a life ♪
